      <title>因流媒体挑战，标准普尔将派拉蒙全球的信用评级下调至“BB+”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/sp-cuts-paramount-globals-credit-rating-bb-streaming-challenges-2024-03-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[评级机构标准普尔周三将派拉蒙全球的信用评级从“BBB-”下调至“BB+”，因为流媒体领域的激烈竞争给这家媒体巨头的自由运营现金流（FOCF）带来了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/sp-cuts-paramount-globals-credit-rating-bb-streaming-challenges-2024-03-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:44:32 GMT</pubDate>
